parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the Autopilot system can cause the vehicle to suddenly slow down or brake without warning, which can lead to accidents or near-misses.
symptoms: The vehicle suddenly slows down or brakes without warning
even when there are no obstacles or vehicles in front of it.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Phantom braking can cause the vehicle to suddenly slow down or brake without warning, which can lead to accidents or near-misses.
symptoms: The vehicle suddenly slows down or brakes without warning
even when there are no obstacles or vehicles in front of it.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the cruise control system can cause the vehicle to suddenly slow down or brake without warning, which can lead to accidents or near-misses.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Lane Departure Warning and Forward Collision Warning
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the lane departure warning and forward collision warning systems can cause the vehicle to suddenly brake or steer without warning, which can lead to accidents or near-misses.
symptoms: The vehicle suddenly brakes or steers without warning
even when there are no obstacles or vehicles in front of it.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden and unexpected braking of the vehicle can cause accidents, injuries, or fatalities, especially if other vehicles are following closely behind.
symptoms: The vehicle suddenly brakes or decelerates without any apparent reason
often when using adaptive cruise control or autopilot features. This can occur on highways
and may be accompanied by a sudden loss of speed or a jolt.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden and unexpected acceleration of the vehicle can cause accidents, injuries, or fatalities, especially if the vehicle is in a confined space or traveling at high speeds.
symptoms: The vehicle suddenly accelerates without any apparent reason
often when using cruise control or autopilot features. This can occur on highways
and may be accompanied by a sudden loss of control or a jolt.
